Partitioning design (in progress)
What the cheminformatics author proposed (partitioningv2.docx):

Dedicate cgpu01 + gpu01 to cheminformatics exclusively
Workload-class partitions: services, dev-gpu, dev-cpu (Both), interactive (Both)
QoS scheme: always-on (2000), services (1000), interactive (300), dev (100), batch (50)
